    <item>
      <title>银行家准备摆脱拜登并购规则的“重担”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-08/bankers-ready-to-shed-weight-vest-of-biden-m-a-rules-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Perella Weinberg Partners 首席执行官安德鲁·贝德纳 (Andrew Bednar) 表示，随着唐纳德·特朗普即将上任的政府承诺解除拜登总统任期内加重该行业的监管“重担”，华尔街交易员将迎来并购热潮。他在“彭博未平仓合约”上发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-08/bankers-ready-to-shed-weight-vest-of-biden-m-a-rules-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 18:42:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾伯塔省任命养老金管理公司临时首席执行官，寻求​​削减成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/alberta-names-interim-ceo-for-pension-manager-after-shock-firing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在整个董事会和首席执行官突然被解雇后，艾伯塔省政府试图削减投资成本，大幅增加主权财富基金的规模，因此任命一位长期任职的官僚为公共养老基金管理公司的临时负责人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/alberta-names-interim-ceo-for-pension-manager-after-shock-firing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 17:38:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
